item.title: Great day hiking with Travis and Yumi!
item.description: 21:56 Friday 01 January 2016 JST So tired. We hiked 16 kilometers, ascending (and descending) the 1610 meter 滝子山, Mt Takigo, though I don’t know from what elevation we started. Great to chill (haha) with Travis and Yumi!
